Subject: [security bulletin] HPSBUX03337 SSRT102066 rev.1 - HP-UX Apache Web Server Suite running Apache Web Server, Tomcat v6.x, or PHP v5.4.x, Remote Denial of Service (DoS) and Other Vulnerabilities

